latestIgtvVideos.title: Traveling During Pandemic!!!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
As you all know finally my Movie Amaram Akhilam Prema is released and I had to travel for promotions and this was the first time I was traveling after 7 months also you all know How much we love traveling as a family. So finally me and mum took a flight to Hyd and I had to share my experience, if you are someone who isn't that scared of everything around you and you not clumsy like me I think Airports and Flights are really safe I mean they taking all the precautions and everything that is possible. I actually told everyone that if I get a chance I would travel again because traveling is safe, now when you reach a destination from there you need to take care by yourself . 

I couldn't shoot much because of my busy schedule and now I am back ! Also While coming back I dint get Blur shield , got the perfect one!! 

Love and Happiness!!
Wish to travel soon without these masks and shield !!!

Letter to My Younger Self,

Hey,

Thank you for never giving up, even when everything felt impossible. Thank you for crying, breaking, healing—and getting back up every single time. You didn’t realize it then, but you were always enough.

I wish you could see the life waiting for you. You’ll feel content, truly content. You’ll have people who love you deeply and value you for exactly who you are. You’ll still feel things deeply, but you’ll have your sisters to hold you through it all.

Mom and Dad? They’re still so proud of you, still pampering you like the queen you are (yes, you’re their favorite, don’t doubt it). And you? You’ve learned to love your imperfect, beautiful self.

Life is full of warmth, love, and joy now. And the best part? The best is still yet to come.

Happiest 32nd to me. To everyone who made today so special—thank you for teaching me how to Live in Present and enjoy the little joys. 

I am so grateful to each one of YOU , you guys mean the world to me. 

Thankful, Grateful and Blessed🧿🩵🥹

Love,
Me
